            >
              Predictive Stocking
            </div>
            <p class="text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-slate-700 font-medium">
              "Your analytics show a 40% uptick in festive categories. To
              maximize
              <span class="text-slate-900 font-bold">Christmas sales</span>, I
              recommend stocking
