                >Smart Home Lights</span
              > by Nov 10th."
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span
              class="text-[9px] bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-bold"
              >↑ Trending Product</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-[9px] bg-orange-50 text-orange-600 px-2 py-1 rounded-md font-bold"
              >⚡ Seasonal Opportunity</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
